dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Adams County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Adams_LandUse_2015.gdb.[(NCWRPC NOTES)This layer has landuse attributes for 2010, 2013 and 2015. We took the Lu2010 layer and added the lu2013 for certain town plans and updated certain towns. We added the lu2015 and used NAIP 2015 spring flight and updated county wide.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Adams County Register of Deeds/Land Records
